The Devilworx - Devilworx

The Devilworx is the name of a Greek experimental symphonic deathcore band which was founded by members of Septic Flesh. Apart from Chris,Seth and Fotis,the band includes Kostas and Jim.The Devilworx were created in 2004 and in the next year they opened the Slipknot concert in Athens...
